short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Voi Wallet Extension | Send & Receive Voi | Sign dApp Transactions

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is a Voi and Algorand wallet extension that lets you send, receive and sign transactions on multiple networks. This is a modified "Algosigner" extension, originally made by Purestake.
